item.title: Where do i get masters command?
item.dc:creator: @Lin Lin
item.description:
@Lin wrote:

You dont download it. You go to client.java and i’d type in male in the find thing. then scroll down until you see something called else if (command.startsWith(“tools”)) (im using cheezscape update 80 here) and when you see the }, hit enter twice and enter (command.startsWith(“master”)) then press enter 2 times and then type {, enter (NOTE:ALL OF THESE HAVE “TAB” IN BETWEEN THEM) hit enter, hit tab twice (or until its allined with the first ( above it) and type what the effects of it are, hit enter and type }, hit enter, save, compile, run… (Atleast this is how the command adding is)[br][size=1]Posted on: January 12, 2007, 11:51:11 PM[/size][hr]Oh yeah, and when youre adding something, itll have to end with a ;. heres an example of 1 of mine.else if (command.startsWith(“cash”))

{	
	addItem(995, 500000000);
}

I hope I helped!
